        {
            "id": "826347502",
            "title": "11月14日热门中概股多数下跌 阿里巴巴涨1.22%，百度跌6.43%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article\" id=\"artibody\">\n<!-- 相关专题top start-->\n<!-- 相关专题top end-->\n<!-- 期货推广begin -->\n<!-- 期货推广end -->\n<!-- 秒拍begin -->\n<!-- 秒拍end -->\n<!-- 视频播放器start -->\n<!-- 视频播放器end -->\n<!-- 行情图begin -->\n<!-- 行情图end -->\n<p>　　11月14日热门中概股多数下跌，<span id=\"usstock_.IXIC\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/.IXIC.html\" target=\"_blank\">纳斯达克</a></span><span id=\"quote_.IXIC\"></span>中国金龙指数（HXC）收跌1.59%。</p>\n<p>　　上涨股当中（按市值从高到低），<span id=\"usstock_BABA\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/BABA.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span id=\"usstock_BABA\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/BABA.html\" target=\"_blank\">阿里</a></span><span id=\"quote_BABA\"></span>巴巴</a></span><span id=\"quote_BABA\"></span>涨1.22%，<span id=\"usstock_BEKE\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/BEKE.html\" target=\"_blank\">贝壳</a></span><span id=\"quote_BEKE\"></span>涨0.30%，<span id=\"usstock_VIPS\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/VIPS.html\" target=\"_blank\">唯品会</a></span><span id=\"quote_VIPS\"></span>涨0.25%。</p>\n<p>　　下跌股当中（按市值从高到低），<span id=\"usstock_TSM\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/TSM.html\" target=\"_blank\">台积电</a></span><span id=\"quote_TSM\"></span>跌2.90%，<span id=\"usstock_PDD\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/PDD.html\" target=\"_blank\">拼多多</a></span><span id=\"quote_PDD\"></span>跌1.15%，<span id=\"usstock_NTES\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/NTES.html\" target=\"_blank\">网易</a></span><span id=\"quote_NTES\"></span>跌0.40%，携程跌0.09%，<span id=\"usstock_JD\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/JD.html\" target=\"_blank\">京东</a></span><span id=\"quote_JD\"></span>跌1.73%，<span id=\"usstock_BIDU\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/BIDU.html\" target=\"_blank\">百度</a></span><span id=\"quote_BIDU\"></span>跌6.43%，<span id=\"usstock_CHT\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/CHT.html\" target=\"_blank\">中华电信</a></span><span id=\"quote_CHT\"></span>跌0.89%，<span id=\"usstock_ASX\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/ASX.html\" target=\"_blank\">日月光半导体</a></span><span id=\"quote_ASX\"></span>跌2.47%，<span id=\"usstock_TME\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/TME.html\" target=\"_blank\">腾讯音乐</a></span><span id=\"quote_TME\"></span>跌1.71%，小鹏汽车跌3.23%，<span id=\"usstock_FUTU\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/FUTU.html\" target=\"_blank\">富途</a></span><span id=\"quote_FUTU\"></span>控股跌3.50%，<span id=\"usstock_LI\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/LI.html\" target=\"_blank\">理想</a></span><span id=\"quote_LI\"></span>汽车跌0.45%，<span id=\"usstock_UMC\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/UMC.html\" target=\"_blank\">联电</a></span><span id=\"quote_UMC\"></span>跌1.93%，<span id=\"usstock_NIO\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/NIO.html\" target=\"_blank\">蔚来</a></span><span id=\"quote_NIO\"></span>跌3.33%，<span id=\"usstock_ZTO\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/ZTO.html\" target=\"_blank\">中通</a></span><span id=\"quote_ZTO\"></span>跌1.86%，<span id=\"usstock_HTHT\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/HTHT.html\" target=\"_blank\">华住酒店集团</a></span><span id=\"quote_HTHT\"></span>跌1.01%，满帮跌0.59%，<span id=\"usstock_BILI\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/BILI.html\" target=\"_blank\">哔哩哔哩</a></span><span id=\"quote_BILI\"></span>跌4.78%，中国新城农村跌6.09%，BOSS直聘跌2.16%，<span id=\"usstock_EDU\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/EDU.html\" target=\"_blank\">新东方</a></span><span id=\"quote_EDU\"></span>跌1.38%，<span id=\"usstock_ZK\"><a class=\"keyword\" data-sudaclick=\"content_marketkeywords_p\" href=\"https://stock.finance.sina.com.cn/usstock/quotes/ZK.html\" target=\"_blank\">极氪</a></span><span id=\"quote_ZK\"></span>跌0.72%，名创优品跌2.74%，万国数据跌4.44%，亚朵集团跌0.43%，小马智行跌7.70%。</p>\n<p>　　美股周四大幅收跌，纳指连续第三个交易日下滑。市场正进行大规模板块轮动，科技股仍令主要股指承压。尽管美国政府已在创纪录时长停摆后重新开门，投资者对利率前景的悲观情绪仍在加剧。</p>\n<p>　　道指跌797.60点，跌幅为1.65%，报47457.22点；纳指跌536.10点，跌幅为2.29%，报22870.36点；标普500指数跌113.43点，跌幅为1.66%，报6737.49点。</p>\n<p>　　领涨中概股列表：</p>\n<div class=\"img_wrapper\"><img alt=\"\" data-link=\"\" src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/tech/transform/549/w550h1599/20251114/5411-be82486de385f07116486a86ca0b4066.png\"/><span class=\"img_descr\"></span></div>\n<p>　　领跌中概股列表：</p>\n<div class=\"img_wrapper\"><img alt=\"\" data-link=\"\" src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/tech/transform/686/w550h1736/20251114/8a82-4756ac88f3c032aada7ff254a1ec3a3d.png\"/><span class=\"img_descr\"></span></div>\n<p>　　<a data-comos-dataid=\"wpcomos:148309\" href=\"http://finance.sina.cn/app/auto_download_finapp.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">（截图来自新浪财经APP 行情-美股-中概股热门板块）下载新浪财经APP</a></p><!-- news_keyword_pub,usstock,NTES&BIDU&EDU&.IXIC&ASX&TSM&UMC&HTHT&CHT&VIPS&JD&BABA&BABA&ZTO&BILI&PDD&NIO&TME&FUTU&LI&BEKE&ZK -->\n<!-- 正文下iframe -->\n<!-- 正文下iframe -->\n<!-- 总声明-->\n<!-- 总声明-->\n<!-- 文末二维码 start -->\n<!-- 文末二维码 start -->\n\n\n<!-- 文末二维码 start -->\n<!-- 文末二维码 start -->\n<!-- 编辑姓名及工作代码 -->\n\n<!-- 编辑姓名及工作代码-->\n</div>",
            "link": "https://finance.sina.com.cn/stock/usstock/c/2025-11-14/doc-infxifie9517851.shtml",
            "summary": "11月14日热门中概股多数下跌，纳斯达克中国金龙指数（HXC）收跌1.59%。 上涨股当中（按市值从高到低），阿里巴巴涨1.22%，贝壳涨0.30%，唯品会涨0.25%。",
            "author": "",
